      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presented in exemplary, showroom condition, this vehicle represents the pinnacle of automotive preservation. Every surface, from the flawless exterior finish to the meticulously maintained cabin, adheres to the highest standards of excellence. Mechanically beyond reproach and accompanied by a comprehensive service history, this is a rare opportunity for the discerning collector to acquire a truly peerless example.",
      "price": 48500.0,
